humin
=====

converts seconds to human readable format. inspired by z3bra's human(1): http://git.z3bra.org/human/file/README.html.

installation
------------

to build humin:

	$ make

to install humin (default location is /usr/local/bin)

	# make install
	
to install to custom PREFIX (binary in this example is installed to /home/me/bin)

	$ make PREFIX=/home/me install 

uninstall humin (add PREFIX option like above to uninstall from custom location)

	# make uninstall
usage
-----

convert 300 seconds to 'hh:mm:ss'

	$ humin 300
	00:05:00

convert 87000 seconds to 'dd days hh:mm:ss'

	$ humin 87000
	01 days 00:10:00

